reviewText: Love it! fantastic voice and received very quickly.

I can't remember where or when I was introduced to the music of Patrick Fiori, but I enjoyed this concert DVD. It did not disappoint and I enjoyed all the songs. Quality entertainment all the way . . . a great addition to any french collection.

The DVD is for PAL System. When I buy the concert I tryed to be sure that it wasn't PAL and it didn't say it anywhere. So now I have the concert that I believe it is really good concert but I can't play it in my player cuz is for PAL.
